Most people weren't lucky.

554
01:08:35,528 --> 01:08:38,816
一年以后，我们从地下出来
So, a year later, we started coming out,

555
01:08:39,365 --> 01:08:40,571
人们徘徊着
and people wandered around.

556
01:08:40,658 --> 01:08:46,528
我不知道要做什么 只想找个地方活下来
I, not knowing what I was gonna do, trying to find a place to survive.

557
01:08:47,832 --> 01:08:50,539
一天我听到了一个声音
One day, I heard a voice.

558
01:08:51,878 --> 01:08:54,790
很难解释，但它听起来像
It's hard to explain, but it was like it...

559
01:08:55,131 --> 01:08:57,747
好像从我内心深处发出来的
Like it was coming from inside of me.

560
01:08:58,635 --> 01:09:02,878
但我可以听到它 就好像我听到你跟我说话这样清楚
But I could hear it as clear as I can hear you talking to me now.

561
01:09:03,431 --> 01:09:05,387
那个声音说了什么？
What did this voice say?

562
01:09:05,933 --> 01:09:07,264
它指引我
It led me

563
01:09:08,186 --> 01:09:10,723
去一个地方，我找到了这本书
to a place where I found the book

564
01:09:11,105 --> 01:09:13,266
埋在一些碎石下面
buried under some rubble.

565
01:09:17,236 --> 01:09:21,024
那个声音告诉我把这本书带到西方
The voice told me to carry the book out west.

566
01:09:22,492 --> 01:09:26,155
告诉我有条路会指引我
Told me that a path would be laid out for me,

567
01:09:26,245 --> 01:09:30,830
我会被带到一个 使这本书会安全的地方
that I'd be led to a place where the book was safe.

568
01:09:34,545 --> 01:09:36,752
它告诉我，会有人保佑我
Told me that I'd be protected

569
01:09:38,132 --> 01:09:41,340
任何人或事都阻碍不了我前进
against anyone or anything that stood in my path.

570
01:09:44,514 --> 01:09:46,926
我从那时起就一直在走
I've been walking ever since.

571
01:09:48,434 --> 01:09:52,268
你这么做的原因就是 因为你听到的一个声音告诉你的？
And you did all that because a voice in your head told you to?

572
01:09:53,106 --> 01:09:54,437
是的
Yes, I did.

573
01:09:55,274 --> 01:09:57,060
我清楚当时我听到了什么
I know what I heard.

574
01:09:57,485 --> 01:09:59,225
我也清楚现在我所听到的
I know what I hear.

575
01:09:59,737 --> 01:10:01,568
我知道我没疯
I know I'm not crazy.

576
01:10:02,281 --> 01:10:05,444
我知道没有他的保佑，我永远不会成功
And I know I would've never made it without help.

577
01:10:06,786 --> 01:10:09,323
- 那是什么？ - 太多问题了
- What's that? - One question too many.

578
01:10:09,789 --> 01:10:12,906
睡觉吧 我们早上要很早上路
Go to bed, we got an early start in the morning.

579
01:10:50,580 --> 01:10:51,660
嘿
Hey.

580
01:11:03,718 --> 01:11:04,798
嘿
Hey.

581
01:11:10,433 --> 01:11:12,515
凯马特-你好，我叫艾利

582
01:11:15,188 --> 01:11:16,928
你在做什么？
What are you doing?

583
01:11:17,315 --> 01:11:19,806
- 抱歉，我以为你在睡觉 - 我没睡
- I'm sorry, I thought you were sleeping. - I wasn't sleeping.

584
01:11:19,901 --> 01:11:21,641
你在做什么？
What are you doing?

585
01:11:22,278 --> 01:11:23,814
我只是想看看那本书
I just wanted to see the book.

586
01:11:23,905 --> 01:11:26,863
除了我谁也不能碰它，你明白吗？
Nobody touches it but me, you understand me?

587
01:11:27,533 --> 01:11:29,069
你听明白了吗？
Do you understand me?

588
01:11:29,160 --> 01:11:31,867
- 是的.我明白 - 好的.去睡觉
- Yes, I understand. - Good. Go to sleep.

589
01:11:41,839 --> 01:11:44,751
你说过你不认识字 它对你没有用
You said you don't know how to read anyway. It's no use to you.

590
01:11:44,842 --> 01:11:45,922
是的
Yeah.

591
01:11:46,969 --> 01:11:48,379
那教我读
So teach me.

592
01:12:08,616 --> 01:12:10,777
等等！停！
Hold up. Hold up! Stop!

593
01:12:16,624 --> 01:12:18,956
你说你已经走了30年了，是吗？
You know, you say you've been walking for 30 years, right?

594
01:12:19,043 --> 01:12:20,249
是的
Right.

595
01:12:20,795 --> 01:12:22,376
你想过你可能迷路了吗？
Have you ever thought that maybe you were lost?

596
01:12:22,463 --> 01:12:23,578
没有
Nope.

597
01:12:23,923 --> 01:12:26,005
你怎么知道你走的方向是正确的？
Well, how do you know that you're walking in the right direction?

598
01:12:26,092 --> 01:12:28,549
“我们行事为人，是凭着信心 不是凭着眼见”
"We walk by faith, not by sight."

599
01:12:29,595 --> 01:12:30,801
那是什么意思？
What does that mean?

600
01:12:30,888 --> 01:12:34,506
是你知道它是正确的 尽管还没有被证明
It means that you know something, even if you don't know something.

601
01:12:34,600 --> 01:12:35,680
这完全说不通
That doesn't make any sense.

602
01:12:35,768 --> 01:12:37,724
没必要说得通，这是信仰 是信仰
Doesn't have to make sense, it's faith. It's faith.

603
01:12:37,812 --> 01:12:40,804
在一片漆黑里，这是光亮的花朵
It's the flower of light in the field of darkness

604
01:12:40,898 --> 01:12:43,355
给了我前进的力量，你明白吗？
that's giving me the strength to carry on. You understand?

605
01:12:43,442 --> 01:12:44,682
这是书里的？
Is that from your book?

606
01:12:44,777 --> 01:12:48,736
不，是强尼卡什在福尔松监狱的演唱
No, it's Johnny Cash live at Folsom Prison.

607
01:12:49,448 --> 01:12:50,528
什么？
What?

608
01:13:13,347 --> 01:13:16,510
- 你认为有人住在那里吗？ - 不知道
- Do you think anyone lives there? - I don't know.

609
01:13:18,227 --> 01:13:19,967
也许那儿有水
Maybe there's water.

610
01:13:29,864 --> 01:13:31,400
待在我后面
Stay behind me.

611
01:13:31,866 --> 01:13:36,485
禁止擅自闯入

612
01:13:36,621 --> 01:13:38,111
这有点奇怪
This is weird.

613
01:14:13,324 --> 01:14:14,689
你们是谁？
Who are you?

614
01:14:18,454 --> 01:14:21,196
我们只是过路的 不是坏人
We're travelers, that's all. Don't mean any harm.

615
01:14:21,290 --> 01:14:24,123
禁止擅自闯入！你没看到标志吗？
No trespassing! Haven't you read the sign?

616
01:14:25,044 --> 01:14:27,456
对不起，我没看到
We're very sorry. I didn't see it.

617
01:14:27,922 --> 01:14:29,128
你在这儿干什么？
What's your business?

618
01:14:29,215 --> 01:14:30,295
- 是... - 没事！
- We were just... - No business!

619
01:14:30,383 --> 01:14:34,797
只是，我们非常抱歉 如果你们允许，我们这就离开
Just... We're very sorry, and if you let us, we'll be on our way.

620
01:14:35,513 --> 01:14:38,880
乔治，看他们 其中一个只是个小姑娘
George, look at them. One of them is just a girl.

621
01:14:38,975 --> 01:14:42,888
是的，老生常谈 我已经听过无数遍了
Yeah. It's an old story, I've heard it a hundred times before.

622
01:14:43,020 --> 01:14:47,389
我们最近很少有访客来 乔治有点疑神疑鬼
We get so few visitors these days. George is suspicious of everybody.

623
01:14:47,733 --> 01:14:51,396
我是玛莎，你们想喝点茶吗？
I'm Martha. Would you care for some tea?

624
01:15:02,164 --> 01:15:05,031
来点音乐如何？旋律很放松
How about some music? It's so soothing.

625
01:15:05,751 --> 01:15:06,957
乔治！
George!

626
01:15:26,939 --> 01:15:30,431
你觉得怎么样？很好听，请喝
How do you like it? It's nice. Please.

627
01:15:41,078 --> 01:15:45,117
一好喝吗？ - 很好，味道很浓郁
- Is that good? - Good, good. That's... Taste is rich.

628
01:15:49,962 --> 01:15:53,546
你们两个能互相依赖活到现在，真了不起
It's amazing that you two have survived out here all by yourselves.

629
01:15:53,632 --> 01:15:56,874
乔治是一个能工巧匠
Well, now, George is something of a handyman.

630
01:15:59,305 --> 01:16:02,547
他为这个地方干了很多活 使这里更安全
He did a lot of work on this place, making it safe.

631
01:16:02,767 --> 01:16:05,258
我们也许老了，但我们适应性很强
We may be old, but we're resilient.

632
01:16:05,936 --> 01:16:08,928
我们遇到很多人 想从我们这儿抢走这个地方
We've known more than a few who've tried to take this place from us.

633
01:16:09,023 --> 01:16:11,184
- 没错吧，乔治？ 是的，我们遇到过
- Haven't we, George? - Yes, we have.

634
01:16:11,275 --> 01:16:13,891
- 是的 - 我给你们看点东西，过来
- Right. - I wanna show you something. Come on.

635
01:16:13,986 --> 01:16:16,227
乔治，别！现在不行!
George, no! Not now!

636
01:16:17,239 --> 01:16:18,479
过来!
Come on!

637
01:16:21,243 --> 01:16:23,359
- 这些是... - 坟墓？当然
- Are these... - Graves? Sure.

638
01:16:23,662 --> 01:16:25,823
不埋葬他们很不文明
Be uncivilized not to bury them.

639
01:16:25,915 --> 01:16:28,327
另外，这对土地有好处
Besides, it's good for the soil.

640
01:16:29,293 --> 01:16:32,785
快进来，我想我可能会 给你们做点三明治
Come on back inside. I think I might be able to rustle you up some sandwiches.

641
01:16:32,880 --> 01:16:35,166
谢谢，非常感谢
Well, thank you, thank you very much.

642
01:16:35,257 --> 01:16:36,793
- 得走了 - 他们把这些人都杀了
- We gotta go now. - They killed all these people.

643
01:16:36,884 --> 01:16:38,465
不只杀了他们，还吃了他们
They didn't just kill them, they ate them.

644
01:16:38,552 --> 01:16:41,464
- 她的手，她的手在抖 - 太多人肉了，我们走
- Her hands... Her hands were shaking. - Too much human meat. Let's go.

645
01:16:42,139 --> 01:16:44,846
我找到了些肉，我想你们饿了
I found some meat. I hope you're hungry.

646
01:16:45,017 --> 01:16:46,553
没有，谢谢
Nope. No, thank you.

647
01:16:46,644 --> 01:16:49,431
我们得走了
Well, we... We gotta be going.

648
01:16:49,522 --> 01:16:51,729
- 这么快？ - 是的，很抱歉
- So soon? - Yeah, I'm afraid so.

649
01:16:51,816 --> 01:16:54,432
- 你确定你不留下？ - 我肯定，非常肯定
- Are you sure you won't stay? - I'm sure, I'm very sure.

650
01:16:54,527 --> 01:16:56,313
把枪放下
Put the gun down.

651
01:16:56,487 --> 01:16:58,273
索拉娜，你拿着这个 把门打开
Solara, you take this. Open the door for us, please.

652
01:16:58,364 --> 01:17:00,480
- 索拉娜，说感谢你的茶 - 感谢你的茶
- Solara, say thank you for the tea. - Thank you for the tea.

653
01:17:00,574 --> 01:17:01,780
非常感谢你的茶
Thank you so much for the tea.

654
01:17:09,625 --> 01:17:11,286
回到里面去
Go back inside.

655
01:17:15,256 --> 01:17:16,291
乔治，怎么了？
George, what's wrong?

656
01:17:16,382 --> 01:17:18,794
一群武装的强盗
Whole company of armed degenerates, that's what's wrong!

657
01:17:18,884 --> 01:17:20,420
他们把他们引到这里
And they led them straight to us.

658
01:17:20,761 --> 01:17:23,844
- 我刚摆好瓷器 - 去他妈的瓷器！
- I just set out the good china. - Fuck the china!

659
01:17:23,931 --> 01:17:25,137
你还有其他武器吗？
Have you got any more weapons?

660
01:17:25,224 --> 01:17:27,931
武器？给你看看我的武器
Weapons? I'll show you some weapons.

661
01:17:31,355 --> 01:17:33,687
- 你会开枪吗？ - 当然
- Can you shoot a gun? - Of course.

662
01:17:35,025 --> 01:17:36,856
快！快！
Come on, come on!

663
01:17:37,069 --> 01:17:39,151
我们知道你们在里面！
We know you're in there!

664
01:17:40,239 --> 01:17:42,855
出来没人会受伤！
Come on out and nobody needs to get hurt!

665
01:17:47,621 --> 01:17:49,486
我会放你一马！
I'll make it easy!

666
01:17:49,790 --> 01:17:52,577
把索拉娜和书交出来！
Send out Solara with the book!

667
01:17:53,002 --> 01:17:55,584
- 我们怎么办？ - 我知道我他妈的在干什么！
- What are we gonna do? - I know what the fuck I'm doing!

668
01:17:55,671 --> 01:18:00,461
- 等等 - 我只想要这两样，书和姑娘！
- Wait, wait, wait. - That's all I want, the book and the girl!

669
01:18:02,261 --> 01:18:04,126
他们不会出来
They ain't coming out.

670
01:18:29,914 --> 01:18:33,623
该死！趴下！大家趴下！
Shit! Get down! Everybody, get down!

671
01:18:52,228 --> 01:18:54,765
嘿！你听到的那个声音
Hey! You know that voice you heard?

672
01:18:54,980 --> 01:18:56,811
它有没有告诉你这件事？
Did it say anything about this?

673
01:18:56,899 --> 01:18:59,311
我们会活着出去的，我们俩个！
We'll get out alive, both of us!

674
01:18:59,485 --> 01:19:00,975
那我们昵？
What about us?

675
01:19:01,779 --> 01:19:03,519
没提到你们！
Didn't mention you!

676
01:19:12,581 --> 01:19:13,946
停止开火！
Cease fire!

677
01:19:14,833 --> 01:19:16,198
停止开火！
Cease fire!

678
01:19:26,887 --> 01:19:28,878
玛莎？玛莎？
Martha? Martha?

679
01:19:28,973 --> 01:19:32,010
玛莎！玛莎！
Martha! Martha!

680
01:19:35,229 --> 01:19:38,266
- 玛莎 - 到边上去！到那边！
- Martha. - Go in on the side! Over on the side!

681
01:19:38,357 --> 01:19:39,813
你们这帮混蛋！
You bastards!

682
01:19:40,567 --> 01:19:43,604
- 在房子的侧面！ - 你们他妈的这帮混蛋！
- The side of the house! - You fucking bastards!

683
01:19:48,951 --> 01:19:52,364
- 别开枪！别开枪！ - 他们在干什么？
- Hold your fire! Hold your fire! - What are they doing?

684
01:19:52,454 --> 01:19:54,115
没有好事
Nothing good.

685
01:21:08,072 --> 01:21:09,687
书在哪儿？
Where's the book?

686
01:21:16,622 --> 01:21:18,158
看看他的包
Check his pack.

687
01:21:36,809 --> 01:21:38,299
不在这儿
It ain't here.

688
01:21:41,105 --> 01:21:45,940
这是你最后的机会 不交出书，我就把你埋在这儿
This is your last chance. You give it up or I swear I'll bury you out here.

689
01:21:56,829 --> 01:21:58,319
狗娘养的
Son of a bitch.

690
01:21:58,664 --> 01:22:00,450
我们再试试
Let's try this again.

691
01:22:05,170 --> 01:22:07,126
- 卡内基！ - 什么？
- Carnegie! - What?

692
01:22:17,307 --> 01:22:20,799
书在哪儿？
Now, where's the book?

693
01:22:26,024 --> 01:22:28,060
把书给他吧，拜托
Give him the book, please.

694
01:22:32,906 --> 01:22:34,521
别告诉他
Don't tell him.

695
01:22:43,542 --> 01:22:46,784
在房子里，电视机后面
It's in the house, back of the TV.

696
01:22:49,006 --> 01:22:50,587
检查电视机！
Go check the TV!

697
01:22:51,216 --> 01:22:52,501
什么？
The what?

698
01:22:52,968 --> 01:22:56,677
你他妈的在开什么玩笑！你，去！
You're fucking shitting me. You, go! Go!

699
01:23:33,050 --> 01:23:36,258
无论求什么，只要信，就必得着
Ask, and you shall receive.

700
01:23:41,767 --> 01:23:43,632
上帝是好人，是吗？
God is good, is he not?

701
01:23:45,187 --> 01:23:46,643
一直是
All the time.

702
01:23:49,024 --> 01:23:50,639
不是一直
Not all the time.

703
01:24:17,010 --> 01:24:18,921
不！不！
No! No!

704
01:25:04,516 --> 01:25:05,756
你现在明白了？
You see?

705
01:25:08,020 --> 01:25:09,681
我怎么告诉你的？
What did I tell you?

706
01:25:15,694 --> 01:25:17,309
他只是个人
He's just a man.

707
01:25:21,199 --> 01:25:23,815
不！把他放了！
No! Leave him alone!

708
01:25:24,536 --> 01:25:26,117
求求你，住手！
Please, stop!

709
01:25:32,711 --> 01:25:34,827
你的保护神在哪?
Where's your protection now?

710
01:25:49,895 --> 01:25:51,305
为我祈祷
Pray for me.

711
01:25:54,816 --> 01:25:55,896
可以吗？
Okay?

712
01:26:00,656 --> 01:26:02,021
我认真的
I mean it.

713
01:27:20,235 --> 01:27:21,315
不！
No!

714
01:27:29,202 --> 01:27:30,487
狗屎！
Shit!

715
01:27:31,997 --> 01:27:33,407
回去！
Go back!

716
01:28:17,209 --> 01:28:19,040
快！快！
Come on! Come on!

717
01:29:18,603 --> 01:29:22,687
我们剩的油刚刚可以回去 你想去追她吗？
We barely got enough fuel to make it back. You wanna go after her?

718
01:29:24,109 --> 01:29:25,144
不
No.

719
01:30:46,399 --> 01:30:50,893
- 你要往哪儿走？ - 我要去西边，必须去西边
- Where are you going? - I'm going west. Gotta go west.

720
01:30:53,615 --> 01:30:54,695
嘿！
Hey!

721
01:31:01,915 --> 01:31:03,030
来
Here.

722
01:31:20,225 --> 01:31:21,556
对不起
I'm sorry.

723
01:31:22,102 --> 01:31:23,558
对不起什么？
For what?

724
01:31:24,187 --> 01:31:26,473
- 这，这都是我的错 - 不，不是的
- This. This is all my fault. - No, it's not.

725
01:31:26,564 --> 01:31:30,807
不，是我的错，如果我不跟着你 这些就不会发生了
No, it is. If I didn't come with you, none of this would've happened.

726
01:31:31,653 --> 01:31:33,393
这不是你的错
It's not your fault.

727
01:31:36,074 --> 01:31:37,814
我做了必须要做的事
I did what I had to do.

728
01:31:37,909 --> 01:31:41,367
我认为任何事情都不能使你放弃那本书
I didn't think anything could make you give up that book.

729
01:31:41,454 --> 01:31:43,911
我以为它太重要了
I thought it was too important.

730
01:31:46,501 --> 01:31:50,585
这么多年，我背着它 每天阅读
All the years I've been carrying it and reading it every day.

731
01:31:52,424 --> 01:31:55,336
我只痴迷于想保护它
I got so caught up with keeping it safe,

732
01:31:55,427 --> 01:31:59,716
我忘了靠从中学到的去生活
I forgot to live by what I learned from it.

733
01:32:00,849 --> 01:32:02,760
是的，那是什么？
Yeah, and what's that?

734
01:32:03,768 --> 01:32:04,928
只是...
Just...

735
01:32:08,273 --> 01:32:11,390
帮助他人要多于帮助自己
Do for others more than you do for yourself.

736
01:32:13,695 --> 01:32:16,311
这是我从中学到的
That's what I got from it, anyway.

737
01:33:02,911 --> 01:33:04,447
你闻到7吗？
You smell that?

738
01:33:05,497 --> 01:33:07,328
- 什么？ - 空气中的味道？
- What? - In the air?

739
01:33:07,457 --> 01:33:08,663
盐？
Salt?

740
01:33:13,379 --> 01:33:15,870
我们靠近大海了
We're getting close to the ocean.

741
01:34:14,899 --> 01:34:19,775
到了
That's it.

742
01:34:52,854 --> 01:34:54,469
把机械师叫来！
Get the Engineer!

743
01:36:26,572 --> 01:36:28,233
别再靠近！
That's far enough!

744
01:36:29,534 --> 01:36:31,616
你们在这里干什么？
What's your business here?

745
01:36:33,121 --> 01:36:34,657
我叫艾利
My name is Eli!

746
01:36:35,540 --> 01:36:38,407
我有一本英王詹姆士版的圣经
I have a King James Bible in my possession.

747
01:36:38,501 --> 01:36:39,991
待在那里！
Remain where you are!

748
01:36:40,086 --> 01:36:44,170
别试图有什么动作 否则就开枪！
Don't attempt to make any sudden moves, or you will be fired upon!

749
01:37:01,065 --> 01:37:04,432
小心！小心！
Be careful with it. Be careful.

750
01:37:11,242 --> 01:37:12,857
小心
Careful with it.

751
01:37:22,962 --> 01:37:24,452
他们没有武器
They're clean.

752
01:37:25,757 --> 01:37:28,590
我们做这件事已经很久了
We've been doing this for a long time now.

753
01:37:30,762 --> 01:37:34,095
- 感觉像一座博物馆 - 不是，比博物馆更好
- Feels like a museum. - No, it's much more than that.

754
01:37:34,557 --> 01:37:37,344
这里是我们重新开始的地方
This is where we're going to start again.

755
01:37:38,061 --> 01:37:41,849
我们有一个印刷机 它很快就可以工作了
We've got a printing press. It'll be operational quite soon.

756
01:37:41,939 --> 01:37:45,352
我们准备教导人们 让他们了解那个失去的世界
We're going to teach people about the world they lost.

757
01:37:45,443 --> 01:37:47,650
帮助他们重建
Help them start to rebuild it.

758
01:37:47,737 --> 01:37:52,151
我是指，你看，莎士比亚 大百科全书，只少了几卷
I mean, look. Shakespeare. Britannica, missing only a few volumes.

759
01:37:52,408 --> 01:37:56,151
这是一整套莫扎特和瓦格纳的唱片
There's a whole series of beautiful Mozart and Wagner records

760
01:37:56,245 --> 01:37:58,486
还保存得很好
in still very pristine condition.

761
01:37:58,581 --> 01:38:01,288
但就是没有圣经，不过现在有了
But never a Bible. Well, not until now.

762
01:38:02,210 --> 01:38:05,122
我能问一下它是什么状况？
Well, may I ask what condition it's in?

763
01:38:06,839 --> 01:38:08,295
它很破旧了
It's beat up,

764
01:38:09,258 --> 01:38:11,123
但还能用
but it will do the job.

765
01:38:11,969 --> 01:38:14,881
- 我可以看一下吗？ - 是的，可以
- Do you think I could see it? - Yes, you may.

766
01:38:22,730 --> 01:38:25,142
- 好了，打开了 - 你打开了吗？
- That's it. It's open. - You there?

767
01:38:59,767 --> 01:39:01,303
你有什么要写的吗？
Do you have anything to write on?

768
01:39:01,394 --> 01:39:04,352
可以给我们一些纸吗？
Could you get us some writing paper, please?

769
01:39:05,022 --> 01:39:06,603
很多纸
And a lot of it.

770
01:39:08,151 --> 01:39:09,812
很多很多
A whole lot of it.

771
01:39:10,862 --> 01:39:12,227
难以置信
It can't be.

772
01:39:13,865 --> 01:39:14,854
这...
It...

773
01:39:19,996 --> 01:39:21,577
这不可能！
It's impossible!

774
01:39:23,291 --> 01:39:24,701
这不可能！
It can't be!

775
01:39:27,879 --> 01:39:31,371
仔细点记下
Pay close attention and write down

776
01:39:33,176 --> 01:39:34,882
我说的每一句话
everything I say

777
01:39:36,220 --> 01:39:39,007
我说的每个字
exactly as I say it.

778
01:39:43,686 --> 01:39:45,768
“摩西的第一卷书
"The first book of Moses.

779
01:39:48,900 --> 01:39:50,515
“叫《创世记》
"Called Genesis.

780
01:39:51,277 --> 01:39:54,440
“第一章，第一节
"Chapter one, verse one.

781
01:39:58,367 --> 01:40:00,107
“起初
"In the beginning,

782
01:40:01,412 --> 01:40:03,368
“上帝创造天
"God created the heavens

783
01:40:05,500 --> 01:40:07,081
“地
"and the earth.

784
01:40:11,005 --> 01:40:12,336
“第二节
"Verse two.

785
01:40:14,759 --> 01:40:18,718
“地是空虚
"And the earth was without form

786
01:40:21,849 --> 01:40:23,180
“混沌
"and void.

787
01:40:28,022 --> 01:40:29,558
“渊面
"And darkness

788
01:40:31,734 --> 01:40:34,646
“黑暗
"was upon the face of the deep.

789
01:40:38,324 --> 01:40:40,406
“上帝的灵
"And the Spirit of God

790
01:40:42,453 --> 01:40:43,909
“运行
"was hovering

791
01:40:46,791 --> 01:40:48,998
“在水面上
"over the face of the waters.

792
01:40:52,838 --> 01:40:54,248
“第三节
"Verse three.

793
01:40:57,969 --> 01:40:59,459
“上帝说
"And God said,

794
01:41:03,724 --> 01:41:05,589
“要有光
"'Let there be light.'

795
01:41:10,773 --> 01:41:12,638
“就有了光”
"And there was light."

796
01:41:23,369 --> 01:41:24,984
索拉娜在哪？
Where is Solara?

797
01:41:28,708 --> 01:41:30,039
在外面
Out there.

798
01:41:31,168 --> 01:41:32,499
她自己选的
Her choice.

799
01:41:33,629 --> 01:41:37,417
我试图把她带回来，她拒绝了
I tried to bring her back. She refused.

800
01:41:41,679 --> 01:41:44,091
她拒绝后你做了什么？
What did you do when she refused?

801
01:41:50,479 --> 01:41:52,595
- 读 - 你对我女儿做了什么？
- Read it. - What did you do to my daughter?

802
01:41:52,690 --> 01:41:55,898
- 读！ - 你对我女儿做了什么？
- Read it! - What did you do to my daughter?

803
01:42:14,045 --> 01:42:16,081
你准备好就可以开始了
You can start anytime.

804
01:42:24,597 --> 01:42:25,928
对不起
I'm sorry.

805
01:42:28,684 --> 01:42:31,221
太久了，我不记得了
It's been so long, I don't remember.

806
01:42:38,736 --> 01:42:41,569
- 你必须记得 - 必须？是吗？
- You have to. - I have to? Really?

807
01:42:41,697 --> 01:42:44,234
不，你必须记得，拜托
No, no, no, no. You have to. Please.

808
01:42:47,912 --> 01:42:49,152
你的腿
Your leg.

809
01:42:50,539 --> 01:42:52,495
它已经不疼了
It doesn't hurt anymore.

810
01:42:54,251 --> 01:42:55,741
我能闻到
I can smell it.

811
01:43:10,601 --> 01:43:13,013
你为了那本书这么努力
You worked so hard for that book.

812
01:43:14,522 --> 01:43:17,264
你牺牲了这么多人
You sacrificed so much, so many men.

813
01:43:19,735 --> 01:43:21,771
现在连保护你的人都没了
More than you could spare.

814
01:43:23,781 --> 01:43:27,774
以前那些怕你的人 连你的名字都不敢说
Now all those people who were too scared to even say your name,

815
01:43:27,952 --> 01:43:32,116
他们现在就在楼下，正在破坏酒吧呢 你知道吗？
they're downstairs, tearing up the bar right now. Did you know that?

816
01:43:32,707 --> 01:43:35,323
没有人去阻止他们
And there's no one there to stop them.

817
01:43:36,669 --> 01:43:38,455
而你却病了
And you're feverish.

818
01:43:41,549 --> 01:43:44,882
我想象不出那种感受 梦寐以求的书就在眼前
I can't imagine what it must feel like to have what you want so close

819
01:43:44,969 --> 01:43:48,632
- 而你却无从解读它 - 闭嘴！
- and it might as well be a million miles away. - Stop it!

820
01:43:52,184 --> 01:43:53,924
你要离开我吗？
Are you leaving me?

821
01:43:56,647 --> 01:43:57,853
克劳迪娅？
Claudia?

822
01:44:00,317 --> 01:44:01,682
克劳迪娅？
Claudia?

823
01:44:05,156 --> 01:44:06,521
克劳迪娅！
Claudia!

824
01:44:33,642 --> 01:44:35,132
走开！
Get away! Get away!

825
01:44:35,227 --> 01:44:36,216
这是我的！
It's mine!

826
01:45:55,349 --> 01:45:56,759
亲爱的主
Dear Lord,

827
01:45:57,393 --> 01:45:59,930
感谢你赐我力量和信念
thank you for giving me the strength and the conviction

828
01:46:00,020 --> 01:46:02,807
去完成你交付给我的任务
to complete the task you entrusted to me.

829
01:46:23,294 --> 01:46:26,582
《创世记》

830
01:46:27,381 --> 01:46:33,377
感谢你在充满荆棘的道路上 持续、真诚地指引我
Thank you for guiding me, straight and true, through the many obstacles in my path,

831
01:46:37,725 --> 01:46:39,056
艾利

832
01:46:39,143 --> 01:46:42,681
使我在周围都迷失的情况下 仍然保持坚毅
and for keeping me resolute when all around seemed lost.

833
01:46:43,606 --> 01:46:47,815
感谢你的保护 和这一路上的指引
Thank you for your protection and for your many signs along the way.

834
01:46:49,320 --> 01:46:53,905
感谢那些你使我做过的好事 我对我做的坏事感到抱歉
Thank you for any good that I may have done. I'm so sorry about the bad.

835
01:46:55,951 --> 01:46:59,239
你知道你不需要离开 欢迎你留下
You don't have to leave, you know. You're very welcome to stay here.

836
01:46:59,330 --> 01:47:02,447
- 你会非常安全的 - 谢谢
- You'll be perfectly safe. - Thank you,

837
01:47:03,751 --> 01:47:06,493
但有些事我必须要做
but this is something that I have to do.

838
01:47:11,175 --> 01:47:12,836
你要去哪？
Where will you go?

839
01:47:14,136 --> 01:47:15,216
家
Home.

840
01:47:21,393 --> 01:47:23,725
感谢你让我结交的朋友
Thank you for the friend I made.

841
01:47:23,938 --> 01:47:27,101
请像照看我那样照看她
Please watch over her as you've watched over me.

842
01:47:48,337 --> 01:47:51,374
感谢你最后允许我安息
Thank you for finally allowing me to rest.

843
01:47:51,882 --> 01:47:53,793
我真的非常累
I'm so very tired,

844
01:47:54,510 --> 01:47:57,252
但是我现在平静地安息
but I go now to my rest, at peace,

845
01:47:58,347 --> 01:48:02,010
因为知道我在这地球上活着的时候 所做的是正确的
knowing that I have done right with my time on this earth.

846
01:48:02,601 --> 01:48:07,846
圣经-新英王詹姆士译本 阿尔卡特拉斯印刷

847
01:48:11,026 --> 01:48:12,982
那美好的仗我已经打过了
I fought the good fight.

848
01:48:13,821 --> 01:48:15,561
当跑的路我已经跑尽了
I finished the race.

849
01:48:19,034 --> 01:48:20,649
所信的道我已经守住了
I kept the faith.

